comments: Williams (BOS) makes contact to Warren's (IND) arm after gathering the loose ball.

Teague (BOS) maintains legal guarding position defending Brogdon's (IND) driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Smart (BOS) steps out of bounds at the start of his drive.
